  "id": "019cdfae-c50a-7c21-a2f3-83c44886cf65",
  "content": "## Dashboard REST API Implementation (Track A) — Completed 2026-03-12\n\n### What was built\nFive REST endpoints added to corvia-server at `/api/dashboard/*`:\n- `/status` — service health, store metrics, config summary, traces\n- `/traces` — span statistics and recent events from structured logs\n- `/logs` — filtered structured log entries (service, module, level, limit)\n- `/config` — current server config summary (read-only)\n- `/graph` — knowledge graph edges via GraphStore\n\n### Architecture decisions\n- **No new dependencies**: Health checks use raw TCP/HTTP/gRPC (no reqwest). Trace parsing uses serde_json + chrono already in the dep tree.\n- **Shared types in corvia-common**: `ServiceState`, `ServiceStatus`, `SpanStats`, `TraceEvent`, `TracesData`, `DashboardConfig`, `DashboardStatusResponse`, `LogEntry`, `LogsResponse`, `TracesResponse` — all in `crates/corvia-common/src/dashboard.rs`\n- **Health probing**: `crates/corvia-server/src/dashboard/health.rs` — HTTP (raw TCP GET), gRPC (HTTP/2 preface handshake), TCP (connect-only)\n- **Trace parsing ported from Python**: `crates/corvia-server/src/dashboard/traces.rs` — ported from `tools/corvia-dev/corvia_dev/traces.py` with span-to-module classification, 1-hour window filtering, last-50-events cap\n- **CORS**: `tower_http::cors::CorsLayer::permissive()` added in corvia-cli main.rs for dashboard cross-origin access\n- **Router merged in main.rs**: `app = app.merge(corvia_server::dashboard::router(state))`\n\n### Code review fixes applied\n- RwLock::read() uses `unwrap_or_else(|e| e.into_inner())` for poisoned lock safety\n- `tail_lines` capped at 50MB max file size to prevent DoS\n- `short_timestamp` validates char boundaries before slicing\n- Logs limit param capped at 1000 max\n- Removed unused `GraphQuery.scope` field\n\n### VS Code Extension Retrofit (Task 14)\n- Replaced ~1,477-line HTML blob with thin iframe wrapper pointing at `http://localhost:8021`\n- `pollStatus()` uses fetch to `/api/dashboard/status` instead of shelling out to corvia-dev\n- Added CSP meta tag with `frame-src http://localhost:8021`\n- Removed ghost `corvia.toggleServices` command\n- Fixed panel disposal pattern\n\n### Test coverage\n24 unit tests total: 3 in corvia-common, 21 in corvia-server (6 health, 15 traces)\n\n### Commits\n- corvia repo: `c4811a0` (initial), `4fbe369` (review fixes)\n- workspace repo: `fc635f2` (extension retrofit), `e2d4b32` (extension review fixes)",
